OL,3,C2024 'almost certain' to be hottest
OL,4,Cyear on record
OL,6,FForecasters warned of the potential
OL,7,Ffor "extreme and life-threatening"
OL,8,Fblazes as strong winds fed a fast-
OL,9,Fmoving wildfire.
OL,11,FThe blaze was burning in a region that
OL,12,Fhas seen some of California's most
OL,13,Fdestructive fires over the years.
OL,15,FAccording to the European dataset, as
OL,16,F2023 was 1.48C above pre-industrial
OL,17,Flevels, it is also virtually certain
OL,18,F2024 will be more than 1.5C higher
OL,19,Fthan before the industrial revolution
OL,20,F- and likely more than 1.55C higher.
