OL,3,C2024 'almost certain' to be hottest
OL,4,Cyear on record
OL,6,FThat would mean the world has breached
OL,7,F` temporarily at least ` a key
OL,8,Fthreshold in the fight against
OL,9,Fdangerous climate change.
OL,11,FUnder the Paris climate agreement,
OL,12,Fcountries are committed to action to
OL,13,Flimit temperature rises to "well
OL,14,Fbelow" 2C above pre-industrial levels
OL,15,Fand pursue efforts to keep them to
OL,16,F1.5C, beyond which the most
OL,17,Fdevastating impacts of storms, floods,
OL,18,Fdroughts, heatwaves, nature loss and
OL,19,Frising seas are expected.
