OL,3,C2024 'almost certain' to be hottest
OL,4,Cyear on record
OL,6,FThe data also shows that October 2024
OL,7,Fwas the second-warmest month globally,
OL,8,Fsecond only to October 2023, and was
OL,9,F1.65C above pre-industrial levels.
OL,11,FIt was the 15th month in a 16-month
OL,12,Fperiod that the global average air
OL,13,Ftemperature was more than 1.5C above
OL,14,Fpre-industrial levels.
OL,16,FThe figures come as countries prepare
OL,17,Fto meet for the latest round of UN
OL,18,Fclimate talks, Cop29, in Azerbaijan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
